### Auto-Spin API Tests
### Test the auto-spin functionality

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@apiUrl = {{baseUrl}}/api/spin

### 1. Start Auto-Spin Session
POST {{apiUrl}}/autospin/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "playerId": "test-player-1",
    "spinCount": 5,
    "spinDelayMs": 2000,
    "level": 1,
    "coinValue": 0.10
}

### 2. Check Auto-Spin Status
GET {{apiUrl}}/autospin/status/{{autoSpinId}}

### 3. Get All Auto-Spin Sessions
GET {{apiUrl}}/autospin/sessions

### 4. Stop Auto-Spin Session
POST {{apiUrl}}/autospin/stop/{{autoSpinId}}

### 5. Test Manual Spin (for comparison)
POST {{apiUrl}}/spin
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "level": 1,
    "coinValue": 0.10,
    "betAmount": 25
}

### 6. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
